lead_paragraph: Svetlana Kuznetsova, seeded No. 1, beat Lindsay Davenport, the defending champion, 7-6 (4), 7-6 (5), to reach the Wismilak International final in Bali, Indonesia. Kuznetsova, who won the tournament in 2002 and 2004, will play for the title today against Marion Bartoli of France.
